{"in": {"title": "Questing Lores", "subtitle": "<span id=\"tr_lore_id\">the legend of fangs</span>", "lines": ["SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/fangs/0/jungle-morning.mp3 (no wait)", "TITLE: The Legend of Fangs the Fearless. Scene 1", "NARRATOR: The mouth of a cave in a dense forest. A fierce looking tiger is pacing near the entrance.", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/fangs/0/fangs-roar-001.mp3", "FANGS: That does it! Five days since a good night's sleep. I must do something about this.", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/fangs/0/fangs-shuffle-001.mp3", "FANGS: (fast) What was that?", "SMALL VOICE: (whisper) Worry not, dear Fangs. I will help you.", "FANGS: What? Who said that?", "SMALL VOICE: It was me. Peony.", "FANGS: Puny?", "SMALL VOICE: No. Peony. You have to pronounce the o.", "FANGS: Oh.", "SMALL VOICE: Yes. Like that.", "FANGS: Ah. There you are. What a tiny mouse! Maybe I should just eat you.", "PEONY: Perhaps. Do you think that will help you sleep?", "FANGS: Now that you mention it... No. In fact, I think I might even forget I ate you.", "PEONY: Well, then. What do you think?", "FANGS: Think what?", "PEONY: About listening to me.", "NARRATOR: Fangs rests his chin on his fist and thinks.", "FANGS: OK. I guess you're right. I have nothing to lose by listening to you.", "PEONY: And nothing to gain by eating me.", "FANGS: Yeah. That too.", "FANGS: But why do you want to help me? What's in it for you?", "PEONY: Why don't you ask me this question after you've had a good night's sleep, Fangs?", "FANGS: You bet I will Peony. And you better hope you have a good answer. If this is a trick, it'll be your last.", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/fangs/0/jungle-morning-r.mp3 (no wait)", "PEONY: Snoozlestones.", "FANGS: Hey! What did you just call me?", "PEONY: No. I meant Snoozlestones. You need to find them if you want to sleep.", "FANGS: Noodlebones?", "PEONY: No. Not Noodlebones. Those are dangerous. You need Snoozlestones.", "FANGS: And where do I find them... these Snoozlebones?", "PEONY: Snoozlestones. You can find them out there.", "FANGS: What do you mean out there?", "PEONY: Out there. In the real world. In the city.", "FANGS: Out there?", "PEONY: Yes. Out there.", "FANGS: But I'm not king of the jungle there. I don't even know my way around in the city.", "PEONY: No. Think of this as a chance. A chance to see what it's like when you're not king.", "FANGS: But I like being king.", "PEONY: Then that's all you'll know.", "FANGS: What do you mean?", "PEONY: I mean no Snoozlestones for us then.", "FANGS: (fast) No no. Wait. You know the city, don't you? Can you show me the way?", "PEONY: Yes. In fact, I even know who can help us find Snoozlestones in the city.", "FANGS: Terrific. Let's go. You can be my page. I still get to king over you in the land of unruly men.", "PEONY: And you can always rely on me to help you every way I can.", "FANGS: Well! What are we waiting for? Let's go then.", "PEONY: Not so fast, Tiger. You can't enter a city like this. They don't like stray cats.", "FANGS: I can see why you like it so much.", "PEONY: That's why nobody knows the city better than I do.", "FANGS: Good. You can tell me what to do then.", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/fangs/0/jungle-morning-r.mp3 (no wait)", "PEONY: Well, you could learn to speak like humans for a start.", "FANGS: Like humans?", "PEONY: Yes. Like humans.", "FANGS: Is that even possible?", "PEONY: You'll be surprised. Start with something easy.", "FANGS: Like what?", "PEONY: I don't know... Maybe a greeting. How about \"Good morning\"?", "FANGS: Good moan-ing?", "PEONY: (pause) On second thought... Make it \"Hi there.\"", "FANGS: Hide there?", "PEONY: (pause) Ok. Now we know what we have to work with. How about just \"hello world\" then?", "FANGS: (x-slow) Hello World?", "PEONY: Yes, just like that.", "FANGS: Hello world?", "PEONY: Way to go, Fangs.", "FANGS: I can do anything.", "PEO